definitions.definition: The daughter of Latinus and wife of Aeneas .
A female given name from Latin used since the 17th century. It was fairly popular in the 18th and 19th centuries, but rare today.

main_definition: ( Roman mythology ) The daughter of Latinus and wife of Aeneas .
